one_reviews_text: Very Relaxing with wonderful music. Be sure to experment, I was very surprised with some of the ways to control what was going on around me. Love everything about it. Thank you
review_feedback: Thanks for the amazing feedback and so glad you've enjoyed the experience! This version is a public beta and an official version with more songs, improved art, and more interactive audio features will be coming soon ~ hopefully this spring.

one_reviews_text: Installed it due to the high reviews. I tried various scenes. I was bored out of my mind. I see you can move things with your hands as those same objects float around a moving background in a circular type room to low key and sometimes strange music. It just felt very dull to me, so perhaps I'm missing something.
